## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/stringmapentrystorage">StringMapEntryStorage</a> - Holds the value in a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/stringmapentry">StringMapEntry</a>.

Factored out into a separate base class to make it easier to specialize. This is primarily intended to support <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/stringset">StringSet</a>, which doesn&#39;t need a value stored at all.

Definition at line 69 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/stringmapentry-h">StringMapEntry.h</a>.
